<http://open-services.net/ns/auto/shapes/2.1#hintWidth> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#name> "hintWidth" .
<http://open-services.net/ns/auto/shapes/2.1#hintWidth> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#occurs> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Zero-or-one> .
