<http://open-services.net/ns/auto/shapes/2.1#resourceType> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Property> .
<http://open-services.net/ns/auto/shapes/2.1#resourceType> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#representation> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#Reference> .
