<http://open-services.net/ns/auto/shapes/2.1#modified> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#propertyDefinition> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> .
<http://open-services.net/ns/auto/shapes/2.1#modified> <http://open-services.net/ns/core#readOnly> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
